spring mvc + hib setup:
-------------------------------------
1.create eclipse project
2a)import springs + hib jars using maven pom.xml
2b)need web.xml
add <servlet> for Dispatcher Servlet in web.xml with the path for springs.xml
2c)Provide springs.xml
add bean tag for viewResolver
add bean tag for SessionFactory
add bean tag for DataSource
add bean tag for hibernateTransactionManager


3.we don't have to write Hibernate.xml
[hiberante config has to be written in springs.xml under  <bean> tag for session factory
4.For working with hibernate we need SessionFactory obj.
5.spring will create the obj for SessionFactory.
6.we need to write a bean tag for SessionFactory.
7.For SessionFactory dependency is the data Sources.
8.we need to write a bean tag for the data source.
9.For data source you have to specify driver class name,url,password.
10.for SessionFactory we need to mention the hibernate properties.



  
  Assignments:
-------------
-> spring Rest
provide the validations for all scenarios